special_powers.name: FROM THE GUTTERS TO THE ROOFTOPS
special_powers.description: Rorschach can use Leap/Climb and Stealth.

special_powers.name: NEVER COMPROMISE! NEVER SURRENDER!
special_powers.description: Rorschach can use Perplex, but he can only modify his own combat values.

special_powers.name: MOM TAUGHT ME EVERYTHING
special_powers.description: Silk Spectre can use Charge, Flurry, and Leap/Climb.

special_powers.name: YOU'RE SUCH AN...
special_powers.description: Silk Spectre can make a ranged combat attack as if she had a range value of 6.

special_powers.name: GOGGLES
special_powers.description: Nite Owl ignores other characters' Stealth.

special_powers.name: POCKET LASER
special_powers.description: Nite Owl can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast as if he had a range of 8.

special_powers.name: SMARTEST MAN ON EARTH
special_powers.description: Ozymandias can use Outwit. Ozymandias can use Outwit a second time during your turn, but must be given a power action instead of a free action to use it.

special_powers.name: TRAIT
special_powers.description: The powers of Dr. Manhattan can't be countered.

special_powers.name: ATOMIC MANIPULATION
special_powers.description: Dr. Manhattan can use Barrier, Penetrating/Psychic Blast, and Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: THAT DIDN'T KILL OSTERMAN...
special_powers.description: Dr. Manhattan can use Impervious, but on a roll of 3-4, instead of the normal effect, you may choose to reduce the damage dealt to 0 and place Dr. Manhattan in your starting area.

special_powers.name: SIMULTANEOUS PERCEPTION
special_powers.description: Dr. Manhattan can use Probability Control and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: STRONGMAN
special_powers.description: Hooded Justice can use Super Strength, but he cannot pick up or carry heavy objects.

special_powers.name: WE HAVE TO STAND TOGETHER!
special_powers.description: When Captain Metropolis is adjacent to a friendly character, modify the defense value of Captain Metropolis and all friendly characters adjacent to Captain Metropolisby +1.

special_powers.name: MILITARY EXPERIENCE
special_powers.description: Captain Metropolis can use Enhancement and Leadership.

special_powers.name: CLEANING UP THE WATERFRONT
special_powers.description: The Comedian can use Charge and Flurry; if the Comedian uses Flurry in the same turn as Charge and targets the same character with both attacks, modify his damage value by -1 for the second attack.

special_powers.name: BEAUTY AND BRAWN
special_powers.description: Silk Spectre can use Charge and Leap/Climb.

special_powers.name: ALWAYS SURROUND YOURSELF WITH GOOD MEN
special_powers.description: Silk Spectre can replace her defense value with the unmodified defense value of an adjacent friendly character.

special_powers.name: SURRENDER TO ME PERSONALLY
special_powers.description: Dr. Manhattan can use Incapacitate. When Dr. Manhattan hits a character with Incapacitate, he deals the character 1 penetrating damage in addition to the normal effect.

special_powers.name: GLIDERS AND RESPIRATORS
special_powers.description: Nite Owl can use the Flight and Swim abilities.

special_powers.name: LEAVE ME ALONE!
special_powers.description: Walter Kovacs can use the Stealth ability.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: RORSCHACH
special_powers.description: Give this character a power action and replace this character with a WM #001 Rorschach on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens from this character, as well as action tokens and pushing damage for this action are applied to the replacement. If replaced, no victory points are awarded for this character and the replacement is considered to be its orange point value for all game effects.

special_powers.name: I READ THE DROPPINGS OF THE CITY
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose a keyword belonging to an opposing character adjacent to Walter Kovacs. Until the beginning of your next turn, modify the attack value of Walter Kovacs or a character friendly to Walter Kovacs by +1 when they attack a character that possesses the chosen keyword.

special_powers.name: STALKER
special_powers.description: Mask-Killer can use Charge, Flurry, and Stealth; when Mask-Killer makes and attack using Charge but not using Flurry, the damage from the attack is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: SWITCHBLADE
special_powers.description: Knot Top can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, but when determining damage any result greater than 3 is reduced to 3.

special_powers.name: MINION: MOB MENTALITY
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the Knot Top keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, modify Knot Top's attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: COMPELLING COMMAND
special_powers.description: Moloch the Mystic can use Leadership; when a friendly character uses an action gained through Moloch the Mystic's Leadership, they can use Willpower until the action is resolved.

special_powers.name: TAKE A DIVE FOR ME
special_powers.description: When Big Figure uses Mastermind, he can deal the damage to an adjacent friendly character with a point value of 100 or less. This damage cannot later be dealt to Big Figure.

special_powers.name: THIS PLACE IS GONNA EXPLODE!
special_powers.description: During your opponent's turn, immediately after a character friendly to Big Figure is defeated, Big Figure or a character friendly to Big Figure can make a close combat attack or a ranged combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: I GOT THE DIRT ON EVERYONE
special_powers.description: Once during your turn, Big Figure can use Outwit or Perplex.

special_powers.name: YOU HOLD 'EM, I'LL HIT 'EM
special_powers.description: When Larry and Mike use the Duo Attack Ability, they may use Probability Control.

special_powers.name: MINION: HENCHMEN
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the Underworld team ability and a higher point value is within 8 squares, Larry and Mike can use Willpower and modifies their damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: THIS IS GETTING HEAVY
special_powers.description: After the resolution of the Duo Attack ability used by The Comedian and Night Owl, roll a d6 and subtract 3 (minimum result 0); place one action token on a number of adjacent opposing characters equal to the result or less. Pushing damage resulting from these tokens is ignored.

special_powers.name: YOU WILL RETURN TO YOUR HOMES
special_powers.description: After the resolution of an attack by Silk Spectre and Dr. Manhattan using the Duo Attack ability, you may place any target successfully hit by the attack in a square of unoccupied terrain up to a number of squares away from Silk Spectre and Dr. Manhattan equal to their speed value.

special_powers.name: NICE OF YOU TO COME ON PATROL WITH ME...
special_powers.description: When Silk Spectre and Dr. Manhattan use the Duo Attack ability, do not modify their damage value by -1 for the second attack.

special_powers.name: ATOMIC FABRICATION
special_powers.description: Silk Spectre and Dr. Manhattan can use Barrier and Super Senses. Once per turn, they can use Barrier as a free action, but can only place two blocking terrain markers.

special_powers.name: SACRIFICIAL LYNX
special_powers.description: If an attack roll targeting Ozymandias and Bubastis doesn't exceed their defense value by 2 or more, reduce the damage dealt by the attack by 2.

special_powers.name: WE MADE A GOOD TEAM
special_powers.description: When Nite Owl and Rorschach use the Duo Attack ability, modify their attack value by +1 for each adjacent opposing character; damage from the second attack made using the Duo Attack ability is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: SPECIAL
special_powers.description: When used as part of a force, Dr. Manhattan can use the Multiattack ability.

special_powers.name: CALM THE CROWD
special_powers.description: After resolving any attack made by Dr. Manhattan on a target character, place an action token on all other opposing characters adjacent to the target that have zero action tokens.

special_powers.name: CLEAR THE SKIES
special_powers.description: Dr. Manhattan can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. After Dr. Manhattan uses Penetrating/Psychic Blast, he can immediately use Pulse Wave as a free action. When using Pulse Wave as a free action, Dr. Manhattan's range value is not halved, but only characters with any of the following symbols have lines of fire drawn to them: {flight},{flight-transport},{giant},{colossal}

special_powers.name: ATOMIC DISASSEMBLY
special_powers.description: Dr. Manhattan can use Invulnerability. Once during your turn, you may give Dr. Manhattan a free action and remove all blocking terrain markers and hindering terrain markers from the battlefield and roll a d6. On a result of 1-2, destroy the nearest 3 objects (including objects carried by opposing characters and those in squares occupied by characters); on a result of 3-4, the nearest area of elevated terrain becomes grounded terrain until the end of the game; on a result of 5-6, the nearest blocking terrain if destroyed.

special_powers.name: LEAVE ME ALONE!
special_powers.description: When the Aspect Dial is turned to reveal this symbol, immediately place Dr. Manhattan in the starting area of the active player's choosing. If any opposing characters occupy that starting area, place them in the starting area furthest from Dr. Manhattan's new position.

special_powers.name: SPECIAL
special_powers.description: When used as part of a force, Dr. Manhattan can use the Multiattack ability.
